            . I am an officer, and took him in charge; he cried, and begged to be let off; I find his parents are very honest people.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I used to work with a young man, who said he would get me a place; he told me to take this plank, and said if I did not he would half kill me.</p>
               <p>The prisoner received a good character.</p>
